name: 1950's Vintage Prom Dress
description: This lovely pink dress from the '50's is perfect for prom, a costume, or another formal occasion. It fits an extra small/size 0-2. There are several layers of tulle, some of the under layers show normal signs of wear but there are no tears or noticeable holes.

name: Vintage Flapper Dress
description:
This vintage flapper dress is a lovely cream color with alternating rows of sequins and fringe. The dress is in good condition, with the only worn parts being the straps. It has been hemmed and hits above the knee.
Tag reads size 14, but fits a size small-medium.
Bust: 36in
Waist: 28in
Hips: 36in

All measurements taken flat & doubled.
